<section id="fs-idm214929808" class="section-summary">
<title>Summary</title>
<para id="fs-idm233761216">Multiple considerations play a role in the selection of the best business structure for each entrepreneur. This decision flows from the entrepreneur’s vision of how the proposed business will operate and affects all aspects of business operations. The decision includes issues related to legal liability, taxation, and the ability to raise capital. This process may also include consideration of the best state to form and operate in, as a result of taxation, regulation, and other related matters.</para>
</section>
