<problem id="fs-idm233771008">
<para id="fs-idm295380112">States can levy a sales tax on items sold online to a customer in a different state if ________.</para>
<list id="fs-idm285318656" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>the business has a nexus with that state</item>
<item>there is a contract between the business and the state comptroller</item>
